<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
C1061: Pump Motor Circuit Performance
</emph>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Pump motor power supply voltage is out of specified range.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Pump motor is activated although pump motor control relay is OFF.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Pump motor is not activated although pump motor control relay is ON.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ESP<sup>®</sup> control module (pump motor) power supply circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ESP<sup>®</sup> control module ground circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ESP<sup>®</sup> control module
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
